 and they will be tormented with fire and sulphur in the presence of the holy angels and the Lamb.
 And the smoke of their torment will go up for ever and ever,
 and neither will they have rest,
 day or night,
 those who worship the creature and his image,
 or if anyone receives the mark of his name.
 This is the patience of the saints,
 who keep the commandments of God and faith in Jesus.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
And I heard a voice from heaven saying:
 ‘Write:
 blessed are the dead who die from this time forward.
 Yes,
 says the Spirit,
